---
title: Cheesy Stuffed Meatballs with Saucy Cavatappi Pasta
description: Sleeves rolled up and hands washed (but still damp)? Let’s get rolling! The trick is to wrap the mozzarella cheese entirely with the meat, so it’s hiding, ready to be discovered when everyone tucks in. Surprise, surprise!
